name: Stem Cell Therapy - Skin Care Product
short_description:
Stem Cells are specialized cells that are able to give rise to more specialized cells, or differentiate into a specific cell type and appear to be one of the body's ablest tools for self-repair. When a disease or injury strikes, these stem cells respond to specific signals and set about to facilitate healing by differentiating into specialized cells required for the body's repair.
